description: The "Currywurst" is a national dish across Germany and has a ‘cult’-following; it has been popular in Germany over a long time: It consists of a Bratwurst type sausage, with added curry-flavored ketchup. There are about 800 Million curry sausages served per year in Germany. The trend in Germany is to offer curry sausage as a more premium fast food experience in a wider variety, e.g. pork, veal, beef sausage as well as different sauces.
name: The No.1 Currywurst Truck
